divs: Sighting Detailslooked out back the object was treetop leval, had bright lights white, and blue, silver solid. It came toward me, flew so fast but I could remember it was like a triangle light in the middle, and on each side and rear. the bottom was round like an egg shape. It was so low I almost could have touched it. it lasted about 1 to 5 mininutes. there was a humming noise as it was going over.one of my cats was in the room with me. she was nervous too.when it came over the roof behind me, it was like it made a beline for me like it knew I was wathing it.
Summary: an object went over my house so low I could see the design and lights.it was not a plane or copter.
